---
import NumberCircle from '../common/NumberCircle.astro';
---

<section>
  <div class='wrapper'>
    <h2 class='lf-semibold'>How We Work</h2>
    <div class='guide'>
      <div class='line'></div>
      <div class='numbers sans-regular'>
        <NumberCircle label='1' />
        <NumberCircle label='2' />
        <NumberCircle label='3' />
        <NumberCircle label='4' />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='container'>
      <span class='tablet-line'></span>
      <div>
        <div class='tablet-num'>
          <NumberCircle label='1' />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class='sans-medium'>Initial Phone Call</h3>
          <p class='sans-regular'>
            Initial Phone Call Our process begins with an initial phone call to
            understand your business needs and objectives. This brief
            conversation helps us gather essential information and determine how
            we can best support your goals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class='tablet-num'>
          <NumberCircle label='2' />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class='sans-medium'>Video Consultation</h3>
          <p class='sans-regular'>
            Next, we conduct a detailed video call consultation. During this
            session, we dive deeper into your business operations, challenges,
            and opportunities, allowing us to tailor our services to your
            specific requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class='tablet-num'>
          <NumberCircle label='3' />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class='sans-medium'>Financial Plan</h3>
          <p class='sans-regular'>
            Following the consultation, we develop a comprehensive financial
            plan. This plan includes budgeting, forecasting, market analysis,
            and strategic recommendations designed to drive your business toward
            its goals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class='tablet-num'>
          <NumberCircle label='4' />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class='sans-medium'>Implement & Grow</h3>
          <p class='sans-regular'>
            Finally, we assist in implementing the financial plan, providing
            ongoing support and adjustments as needed. Our goal is to help your
            business grow efficiently and sustainably, leveraging our expertise
            to ensure long-term success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang='scss'>
  @import '../../styles/variables.scss';

  section {
    background-color: $neutral-light;
    color: $dark;
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .guide {
    display: none;
  }

  .container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;

    > div {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: min-content 1fr;
      grid-gap: 1.5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
  }

  .tablet-num {
    display: block;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .tablet-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 1.3rem;
    top: 10%;
    width: 0.125rem;
    background-color: $dark;
    height: 80%;
  }

  // Above tablet
  @media only screen and (min-width: $tablet) {
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .guide {
      display: block;
      position: relative;
      margin: 0 6rem 2.5rem;

      .line {
        border-bottom: 0.125rem solid $dark;
      }

      .numbers {
        bottom: -1.25rem;
        position: absolute;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        width: 100%;

        span {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
          border: 0.125rem solid $dark;
          border-radius: 50%;
          width: 2.5rem;
          height: 2.5rem;
          background-color: $white;
        }
      }
    }

    .container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      grid-gap: 1rem;

      > div {
        display: block;
      }

      h3 {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
    }

    .tablet-num {
      display: none;
    }

    .tablet-line {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
